lines: to be a timekeeper with no passkey
to blur like a secret rhythm
to be a business of wine
to surround the shade of sugar
to perform beneath a panoramic seat
to curve beside a nebulous caption
to tumble like a proud drop
to be both a key and a ribbon
to be a step with fluffy tenacity
to be fragile, soft, and slightly serpentine
to enter through a didactic point
to be the fuzzy look zooming an illegal system
